(used by the sp and sy objects in MATLAB)

Note that everything in MATLAB uses the non-normalized values The only exception is the sp and sy objects, that have the knots normaled in $[t_{0n}, t_{fn}]$. So whenever these objects return something (vel, accel, jerk,...), these are normalized values, which I need to transform to non-normalized values to be able to use them in MATLAB
